title: Coleman Cable 046408806 6-Outlet Computer Surge Protector with 4-Feet Cord
features: Ideal for high-end home and professional workstations
Great solution for computers, laser printers, and home-theater systems
description: Surge protectors are designed to prevent damage to electronics that come from surges and spikes in electrical currents. This 6-Outlet surge protector was made with your personal computer and office in mind. It protects up to 750 joules and has a 50,000 Connected equipment warranty. It has a Right angle plug to let you move furniture very close to the wall, which also prevents it from being tripped on. Each cover outlet has a safety cover that can slide over the outlet holes and prevent random shock from occurring. It has Automatic Shut-down Protection and the electrical rating is: 15 Amps/125 Volts/1875 Watts. The Clamping Voltage goes up to 330 Volts. it also has EMI/RFI Noise Filtration. It meets and passes strict electrical safety guidelines by UL and CUL
